00:42:59.640 --> 00:43:01.470
around the economic problems that we've had
are seemingly lost. And how do we, you said

00:43:01.470 --> 00:43:12.520
we had to take it more seriously and take
our democracy more seriously. So what ways

00:43:12.520 --> 00:43:17.450
do you suggest that we do that and what is
available to us?

00:43:17.450 --> 00:43:20.280
&gt;&gt;Eric Alterman: Oh, boy. Well, I do try and
